Summary: Library that provides access to the MusicBrainz server
License: LGPL

Packager: Motsyo Gennadi <drool@altlinux.ru>

Url: http://www.musicbrainz.org/

Source: ftp://ftp.musicbrainz.org/pub/musicbrainz/%name-%version.tar.gz
